<?xml version="1.0"?>
<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5">
  <title>ganglia</title>
  <para>The Ganglia module provides Ganglia support for Reconnoiter.  The ganglia modules joins a multicast group and waits for metrics to come from a gmond agent.</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>loader</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>C</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>image</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>ganglia.so</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <section>
    <title>Module Configuration</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>multiaddr</term>
        <listitem>
          <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>required</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>required</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>default</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>239.2.11.71</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>allowed</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>\d+</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
          </variablelist>
          <para>The address of the multicast group from which which ganglia packets are received</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>port</term>
        <listitem>
          <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>required</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>required</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>default</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>8946</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>allowed</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>\d+</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
          </variablelist>
          <para>The port of the multicast group from which which ganglia packets are received</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>multiaddr6</term>
        <listitem>
          <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>required</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>optional</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>allowed</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>\d+</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
          </variablelist>
          <para>The address of the ipv6 multicast group from which which ganglia packets are received</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>port6</term>
        <listitem>
          <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>required</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>optional</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
              <term>allowed</term>
              <listitem>
                <para>\d+</para>
              </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
          </variablelist>
          <para>The port of the ipv6 multicast group from which which ganglia packets are received</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>
</section>
